Qbs Manual List of Built-in Services Qbs 1.22.0  List of Built-in Services   Qbs provides the following built-in JavaScript extensions to simplify operations that are expected to be needed often in project files.
To gain access to the operations provided by a particular Service - for example, the File service - use the following statement at the top of your Qbs project file:
import qbs.File If you instead need to access the service from a JavaScript file, import it using the following statement at the top of your JavaScript file:
